			"updated_at": "2026-01-06T21:38:16Z",
			"body": "Hi @tessus,\n\nThank you for your feedback. I'd like to clarify what was translated in this PR:\n\n1. **Only missing translations were added**: This PR only filled in empty `msgstr \"\"` entries. All existing translations were left unchanged.\n\n2. **Command names were NOT translated**: In the string \"Commands: `add`, `remove`, `list`, `delete`, `accept`, `leave`, and `reject`\", all command names remain in English within backticks. Only the label \"Commands:\" was translated to \"Εντολές:\".\n\n3. **Technical terms were preserved**: Terms like JSON, Markdown, HTML, API, and parameter placeholders like `<item>`, `[notebook]` were kept in English.\n\n4. **Only descriptive text was translated**: For example, \"Prefer JSON output\" → \"Προτιμήστε την έξοδο JSON\" (where JSON stays in English).\n\n5. **I am a fluent Greek speaker** and have verified all translations for accuracy and proper context.\n\nCould you please point out specifically which words you'd like me to change? I want to make sure I address your concerns correctly.\n\nThank you!",
			"author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
