			"updated_at": "2026-01-06T22:22:55Z",
			"body": "Thank you @tessus for pointing that out! You're absolutely right.\n\nI found the issue - in the `command-share` translation, I had incorrectly translated `[notebook]` to `[φορητού υπολογιστή]` and `[user]` to `[χρήστη]`. These are now fixed and kept in English.\n\n**Fixed translation:**\n```\n\"Shares or unshares the specified [notebook] with [user]. Requires Joplin Cloud or Joplin Server.\"\n→ \"Διαμοιράζει ή καταργεί τη διαμοιρασμό του καθορισμένου [notebook] με τον [user]. Απαιτεί Joplin Cloud ή Joplin Server.\"\n```\n\nI verified that all other CLI placeholders (like `<item>` in other commands) are correctly kept in English. I'll push the corrections shortly.\n\nThank you for your thorough review!",
